<p class="BodyText tm20"><span class="tm21"></span><strong><u><span class="tm19" style="font-weight: 400px !important;">SERVICES</span></u></strong><span class="tm21">. Upon successful completion and receipt of all customer enrollment requirements, Company will
supply gas Services for your home or small business. Company is a retail marketer of Services and is not your Utility.</span><span
